{"tid":340110,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"日本旅行吃快餐","createTime":"2017-07-29T15:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T02:23:25.000Z","uid":123103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a56a00af21cfc8f6a6c0549916410163144df4","tid":340110,"uid":123103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"上次就post左係日本吃M記將軍漢堡餐，今次就講下今次日本旅行每日吃既快餐，其實揀快餐既原因都係就腳同費時煩<br />\n<br />\n早餐就吃唔知咩名餐廳，叫左個鰻魚飯早餐，30-40蚊左，鰻魚就一般般<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/233141_968c5f61b748ca99f8a03468e5f65e57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F233141_968c5f61b748ca99f8a03468e5f65e57.jpg&h=67df6f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早餐係酒店附近吃吉野家<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/231930_01865c2933cccfc209225112d0d90ed5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F231930_01865c2933cccfc209225112d0d90ed5.jpg&h=a38b12d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好鐘意日本啲早餐好豐富，又抵食又飽肚，兌返港紙都係30幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n第二日出遠門就去左日本橫濱中華街吃台式排骨飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/232255_a1932ceda88e2b49be520e4084b276ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F232255_a1932ceda88e2b49be520e4084b276ab.jpg&h=095944b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/232256_8065881bdcd195f327b64dff2e6c4faf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F232256_8065881bdcd195f327b64dff2e6c4faf.jpg&h=fba53f36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塊豬扒好酥脆，感覺好似去左台灣，不過飯就唔算多同好油<br />\n<br />\n晚餐都係捒就腳同近近地既松屋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/232522_ddbdc15328e8c73a83931a3f97052e27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F232522_ddbdc15328e8c73a83931a3f97052e27.jpg&h=db74bf92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫左個燒牛肉飯，一般般，吃完都幾飽<br />\n<br />\n今早就係すき家度叫左牛肉飯定食，大約40幾蚊左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/233824_7da47d18869afbafc94abff35c0c634f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F233824_7da47d18869afbafc94abff35c0c634f.jpg&h=0ac28597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/233631_c6d96073871f140e4ae70ca4ca26206f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F233631_c6d96073871f140e4ae70ca4ca26206f.jpg&h=1b81e3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/233733_9d7679c7ab90b0ef2b496cf55781007e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F233733_9d7679c7ab90b0ef2b496cf55781007e.jpg&h=73a710c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蜆肉有啲腥同有沙，一般"},{"pid":"2864449f939d440c2132e18863a628d793504bd9","tid":340110,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一張圖香港食最小要80<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c331badb67c189a1d50bc02c25e2741159fcf68","tid":340110,"uid":123103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T16:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一張圖香港食最小要80<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平民價錢"},{"pid":"1bb24a50caec6cc90c97ccd0cd470c389732bb3a","tid":340110,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"三十蚊個早餐都話抵"},{"pid":"2ac8eed28e2cdf5bae0f04397fe04794c0942eeb","tid":340110,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"